Body: Description: We’ve found two hidden shares on different Nasuni filers we’re unable to audit via FSAA / SDD.  We found only because audit info was requested specifically for these to share.  The auditing tasks are tied to requests and are important to us.  I’ve harvested logs and related info from one filer and attached to this message.  Let me know if there’s additional info you may need to get this troubleshot or working.
What We've Learned Updated: US Customer. Assigning ticket to Dusty Grayson as per technical support notes.
SLA was breached before I joined my shift
I think we will need to verify that they have any options in the query that may be hiding those shares.
